QuestData.Title: My Heart is Full
QuestData.Description:
$n! Can you believe it? We have enough Anima that the Winter Queen can fully restore the Heart of the Forest!
You've done so much for us!
QuestData.LogDescription: Witness the Winter Queen empower the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: We're so grateful for all your help, $n. Seeing the Heart of the Forest like this again, full of power? My heart is filled with hope.
